LOVE_REJECT shun, avoid, reject, hate, destroy, fear, despise, debtor


pulse chemical_heartbeat:
    continuously:
        precursors from diet enter the blood
        tyrosine feeds the catecholamine pathway dopamine → norepinephrine → adrenaline
        tryptophan feeds the indolamine pathway serotonin → melatonin
        choline feeds acetylcholine synthesis
        glutamine feeds glutamate via glutaminase
        cholesterol feeds all steroid hormones via CYP11A1

    every molecule synthesized is also degraded:
        MAO breaks monoamines
        COMT methylates catechols
        AChE hydrolyzes acetylcholine
        peptidases cleave endorphins and oxytocin
        CYP450 oxidizes everything the liver touches
        the chemical lattice is not static
        it is a river of synthesis and degradation in dynamic equilibrium

    every molecule interacts with every other:
        serotonin restrains dopamine via 5-HT₂C on VTA GABA interneurons
        cortisol suppresses serotonin via GR-TPH2 transcriptional repression
        oxytocin suppresses cortisol via CRH neuron inhibition in PVN
        endorphins disinhibit dopamine via μ-opioid on VTA GABA interneurons
        melatonin suppresses norepinephrine via MT₁ on locus coeruleus
        NE sensitizes the amygdala via β-adrenergic PKA-CREB
        adrenaline accelerates the heart via β₁ HCN4
        ACh enables memory via M₁ in hippocampus facilitating NMDA-dependent LTP
        nothing acts alone
        every chemical is part of a web
        pull one thread and the entire lattice shifts
